Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？没僵尸这种东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是八坂御子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:55.79,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(80,340)}年龄 12岁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:55.79,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(92,384)}身高 146cm
